high_descs: Turn around and go to the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the mug in for a few seconds and take it back out.
Turn around and take a left at the stove all the way to the rack.
Set the mug on the shelf of the rack.
anns.task_desc: Chill the mug in the fridge and set it on the rack.

high_descs: Turn to your right then face the coffee maker on your right
Pick up the mug on the coffee maker
Turn to your right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge then put in and out the mug then close the fridge
Turn to your right then across the room head to the shelf beside the table
Put the mug on the shelf beside the plate
anns.task_desc: Put the cold mug on the shelf

high_descs: Turn around and face the coffee pot behind.
Pick the white cup up from the coffee maker.
Go to the right and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the cup in the fridge and shit the door and then open it and take the cup out and shut the door again.
Turn around and go left to stand in front of the brown shelves.
Put the mug down on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup on the shelf.
